OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNumbers on furlough drop to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnew low                    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of people on furlough has   
OL,6, continued to fall, with young people   
OL,7, leading the way, latest figures show.  
OL,9,FAt the end of July, 1.6 million people 
OL,10,Fwere still on furlough, the lowest     
OL,11,Flevel since the start of the pandemic  
OL,12,Fand 340,000 fewer than a month earlier.
OL,14,FBut older people and the travel sector 
OL,15,Fdid less well, with half of eligible   
OL,16,Ftravel workers still on the scheme.    
OL,18,FThe Resolution Foundation said the     
OL,19,Fnumbers of people coming off furlough  
OL,20,Fhad "slowed to a trickle".             
